{"tid":2048334,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)無恐不入","createTime":"2020-06-02T17:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T18:37:34.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1a775b8e13b70a0c0df8fa2339d03ed113a475d3","tid":2048334,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T17:21:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=f84ccfd9\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=6e738240\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=034899dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://theinvasionmovies.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/theinvasion721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinvasionmovies.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F01%2Ftheinvasion721.jpg&h=fda5305e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一艘發射沒多久的太空梭突然在空中解體，碎片掉落在美國德州到華盛頓州之間；這看似意外的太空梭的解體事故背後卻似乎隱藏者一個極大的陰謀。許多民眾在好奇的情況下去觸碰這些太空梭的碎片，甚至有人把撿到的太空梭碎片拿到eBay上面去賣，有一位名叫塔克（傑瑞米&middot;諾森飾演）的民眾也因此不小心被碎片割傷。而塔克在當天睡覺眼球快速轉動週期過後被細菌改變了其身體結構，隔天就變成被細菌完全控制的人..<br />\n<br />\n1 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 播完先算<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=1d9d82d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=aba4f868\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61112db8b5341caf3f7abb6df8725b6f8d312508","tid":2048334,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T17:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccc049eff94af059b9d282d328de450449bfb2f","tid":2048334,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T17:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a25dc98e06c23ee1defffe2b3c44e00ab4e195","tid":2048334,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T18:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src